"citations": ["Dweck, Carol. (2006). Mindset: The Power of Believing You Can Improve."],"safety_notes":"The discussion remains focused on constructive solutions without resorting to harmful generalizations about any group, recognizing the importance of nuanced understanding within the persona's experiences."}
